      "translation": "The Board recommends an increase in the final dividend of 7.5% to HK$1.0030 per share, subject to approval by shareholders at the forthcoming Annual General Meeting of the Company. This brings the total dividend for 2020 to HK$1.3530 per share, representing an increase of 6.9% compared to the total dividend for 2019. This reflects AIA's long-established prudent, sustainable and progressive dividend policy, which enables the Group to capitalize on future growth opportunities while maintaining financial flexibility."
